          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Nonetheless, soon after the bank industry‚Äôs letter, a group of senior Republican House lawmakers ‚Äî including some of the chamber‚Äôs top recipients of banking industry campaign cash ‚Äî parroted the financial industry‚Äôs rhetoric in their own ",
            "type": "text",
