      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "‚ÄúIt‚Äôs certainly ironic that Silicon Valley Bank‚Äôs lobbying groups were trying to shortchange the Deposit Insurance Fund just as their deposits might need to call on it,‚Äù Todd Phillips, a former FDIC attorney, told ",
            "type": "text",
